@startuml AWS Multi-AZ Multi-VPC Architecture
title AWS マルチAZ / マルチVPC 構成 (Prod/Dev 分離 + S3+CloudFront)\nリージョン: ap-northeast-1 / 3 AZ (1a, 1c, 1d)

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName "Noto Sans JP"
skinparam roundCorner 10
skinparam rectangle {
  BackgroundColor<<vpcP>>  #EAF4FC
  BorderColor<<vpcP>>      #1E7CC8
  FontStyle<<vpcP>>        bold
  BackgroundColor<<vpcD>>  #FCEAEA
  BorderColor<<vpcD>>      #C81E1E
  FontStyle<<vpcD>>        bold
  BackgroundColor<<az>>    #F7FAFD
  BorderColor<<az>>        #93B7DD
  BackgroundColor<<pub>>   #FFF5E5
  BorderColor<<pub>>       #E08E00
  BackgroundColor<<priv>>  #F2F2F2
  BorderColor<<priv>>      #888888
  BackgroundColor<<db>>    #E8F5E9
  BorderColor<<db>>        #43A047
  BackgroundColor<<edge>>  #FFFFFF
  BorderColor<<edge>>      #9C27B0
}
skinparam database {
  BackgroundColor #E8F5E9
  BorderColor     #2E7D32
}
skinparam component {
  BackgroundColor #FFFFFF
  BorderColor     #1E7CC8
}
skinparam cloud {
  BackgroundColor #F5F5F5
  BorderColor     #888888
}

actor "User\n(Internet)" as user

' =========== Edge layer (S3 + CloudFront) ===========
rectangle "Edge Layer (Global)" <<edge>> {
  cloud "Route 53\napp.example.com / dev.example.com" as r53
  component "CloudFront-Prod\n(/  → S3-Prod,  /api/*  → ALB-Prod)" as cfP
  component "CloudFront-Dev\n(/  → S3-Dev,   /api/*  → ALB-Dev)"  as cfD
  database "S3-Prod\nUI bucket" as s3P
  database "S3-Dev\nUI bucket"  as s3D
}

' =========== VPC-Prod ===========
rectangle "**VPC-Prod**  10.0.0.0/16" <<vpcP>> {

  component "ALB-Prod\n(Internet-facing,\n SG: CloudFront PL only)" as albP
  component "NAT GW-Prod\n(1a only)" as natP
  component "IGW-Prod" as igwP

  rectangle "AZ ap-northeast-1a" <<az>> {
    rectangle "Public 10.0.0.0/24" <<pub>> as pubPa
    rectangle "App (Private) 10.0.10.0/24" <<priv>> {
      component "App EC2 (ASG)" as appPa
    }
    rectangle "DB (Private) 10.0.20.0/24" <<db>> {
      database "Aurora Writer" as dbPw
    }
  }
  rectangle "AZ ap-northeast-1c" <<az>> {
    rectangle "Public 10.0.1.0/24" <<pub>> as pubPc
    rectangle "App (Private) 10.0.11.0/24" <<priv>> {
      component "App EC2 (ASG)" as appPc
    }
    rectangle "DB (Private) 10.0.21.0/24" <<db>> {
      database "Aurora Reader 1" as dbPr1
    }
  }
  rectangle "AZ ap-northeast-1d" <<az>> {
    rectangle "Public 10.0.2.0/24" <<pub>> as pubPd
    rectangle "App (Private) 10.0.12.0/24" <<priv>> {
      component "App EC2 (ASG)" as appPd
    }
    rectangle "DB (Private) 10.0.22.0/24" <<db>> {
      database "Aurora Reader 2" as dbPr2
    }
  }
}

' =========== VPC-Dev ===========
rectangle "**VPC-Dev**  10.1.0.0/16" <<vpcD>> {

  component "ALB-Dev\n(Internet-facing,\n SG: CloudFront PL only)" as albD
  component "NAT GW-Dev\n(1a only)" as natD
  component "IGW-Dev" as igwD

  rectangle "AZ ap-northeast-1a " <<az>> {
    rectangle "Public 10.1.0.0/24" <<pub>> as pubDa
    rectangle "App (Private) 10.1.10.0/24" <<priv>> {
      component "App EC2 (ASG)" as appDa
    }
    rectangle "DB (Private) 10.1.20.0/24" <<db>> {
      database "Aurora Writer" as dbDw
    }
  }
  rectangle "AZ ap-northeast-1c " <<az>> {
    rectangle "Public 10.1.1.0/24" <<pub>> as pubDc
    rectangle "App (Private) 10.1.11.0/24" <<priv>> {
      component "App EC2 (ASG)" as appDc
    }
    rectangle "DB (Private) 10.1.21.0/24" <<db>> {
      database "Aurora Reader 1" as dbDr1
    }
  }
  rectangle "AZ ap-northeast-1d " <<az>> {
    rectangle "Public 10.1.2.0/24" <<pub>> as pubDd
    rectangle "App (Private) 10.1.12.0/24" <<priv>> {
      component "App EC2 (ASG)" as appDd
    }
    rectangle "DB (Private) 10.1.22.0/24" <<db>> {
      database "Aurora Reader 2" as dbDr2
    }
  }
}

' --- Ingress (User -> CloudFront -> S3 / ALB) ---
user --> r53
r53 --> cfP : app.example.com
r53 --> cfD : dev.example.com

cfP --> s3P : /  (UI static)
cfP --> albP : /api/* (origin)
cfD --> s3D : /  (UI static)
cfD --> albD : /api/* (origin)

' --- ALB -> App -> Aurora (Prod) ---
albP --> appPa
albP --> appPc
albP --> appPd
appPa --> dbPw
appPc --> dbPw
appPd --> dbPw
appPa ..> dbPr1 : read
appPc ..> dbPr1 : read
appPd ..> dbPr2 : read
dbPw <..> dbPr1 : replication
dbPw <..> dbPr2 : replication

' --- ALB -> App -> Aurora (Dev) ---
albD --> appDa
albD --> appDc
albD --> appDd
appDa --> dbDw
appDc --> dbDw
appDd --> dbDw
appDa ..> dbDr1 : read
appDc ..> dbDr1 : read
appDd ..> dbDr2 : read
dbDw <..> dbDr1 : replication
dbDw <..> dbDr2 : replication

' --- Egress (App -> NAT -> IGW) ---
appPa ..> natP
appPc ..> natP
appPd ..> natP
natP --> igwP
igwP --> user

appDa ..> natD
appDc ..> natD
appDd ..> natD
natD --> igwD
igwD --> user

note right of cfP
  **CloudFront**
  - SPA: 403/404 → /index.html
  - /api/* は ALB を origin
  - ACM 証明書は us-east-1
  - WAF (任意) attach
end note

note right of dbPw
  **Aurora Cluster (Prod / Dev 各)**
  - 3 AZ DB Subnet Group
  - Writer 障害時に自動 Failover
  - Cluster / Writer / Reader Endpoint
end note

note right of natP
  **NAT GW は 1a のみ (学習用)**
  - 1a 障害時は App の外向き通信が全断 (SPOF)
  - 検証完了次第、削除すること (時間課金)
end note

note as N1
  **Prod / Dev は完全分離** (VPC Peering なし)
  - SG / IAM / 鍵 / 証明書 もすべて環境別
  - データは Dev → Prod に流さない (リーク防止)
end note

note as N2
  **検証後の削除順**
  CloudFront → ALB → NAT GW (+EIP)
   → Aurora → ASG/EC2 → S3 → VPC → ACM
  詳細は docs/cleanup-checklist.md
end note

@enduml
